        "Alice",
        "Zoe",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个box分别对应交易双方和合约层。那消息流向是Alice直接调用合约的makeTradeInvitation吗？还是说她先跟Zoe交互？",
