      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Alice直接发给合约，用异步消息箭头。合约收到后激活，再异步转发给Zoe调用makeInvitation，把K8s集群信息带过去。Zoe激活后返回一个invitation对象给合约。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-)C",
        "activate C",
        "C--)Zoe",
        "makeInvitation",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "invitation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把前半段画出来了：Alice到合约的makeTradeInvitation，合约激活后转发给Zoe，Zoe激活返回invitation。接下来合约要把邀请回给Alice？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe--)-C",
        "activate C",
        "Invitation toJoin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，合约用Invitation toJoin异步发给Alice，然后合约就可以释放了。关键是下一步：Alice要直接发给Zoe一个offer，带上CloudNative_HelmChart，这里要用创建激活的箭头，因为Zoe已经在运行了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C--)A",
        "deactivate C",
        "A-)+Zoe",
        "offer",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Alice到Zoe的offer是创建激活（+），因为Zoe之前只是被合约激活过一次，现在Alice的消息要让她保持激活状态。然后Zoe内部有个escrow Price pmt的自循环？",
      "elements_involved": [
